This paper is related to information retrieval (IR) as it focuses on the task of term extraction, which is a crucial step in IR. It also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (CL). The use of particle swarm optimization (PSO) techniques suggests that this paper may also be related to machine learning (ML) and optimization (LG). Additionally, the domain of religious documents suggests that this paper may also be related to artificial intelligence (AI) and deep learning (DL) techniques for text analysis.
